    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="d-flex gap-5 align-items-center py-5">
        <div class="w-50">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">
                <span class="border border-primary border-2 rounded px-2 py-1 fw-bold navbar-brand text-primary">
                    MediHaven
                </span>
            </h1>
            <p class="lead my-5">
                Welcome to MediHaven, your trusted partner in health insurance management. We understand that navigating the complexities of the healthcare system can be overwhelming, which is why we're here to simplify the process and ensure you receive the best care possible. Our mission is to provide individuals and businesses with comprehensive health insurance solutions that offer peace of mind and financial protection.
            </p>
            <h2 class="fw-bold mt-5">
                Comprehensive Health Insurance Solutions for Individuals and Businesses
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-3 mb-5">
                At MediHaven, we believe that everyone deserves access to high-quality healthcare. We work closely with reputable insurance providers to offer a wide range of coverage options tailored to meet the unique needs of our clients. Whether you're an individual seeking coverage for yourself or a business owner looking to provide health insurance benefits to your employees, we have the expertise and resources to guide you through the process and find the right plan for you.
            </p>
            <h2 class="fw-bold mt-5">
                Dedicated Professionals Committed to Exceptional Service and Support
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-3 mb-5">
                Our team of dedicated professionals is committed to delivering exceptional service and support. We understand that health insurance can be complex, so we take the time to listen to your needs and answer any questions you may have. We are here to educate and empower you to make informed decisions about your health insurance, ensuring that you have the coverage you need when you need it most.
            </p>
            <h2 class="fw-bold mt-5">
                Transparency, Reliability, and Integrity: Building Trust with our Clients
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-3 mb-5">
                With MediHaven, you can expect transparency, reliability, and integrity. We prioritize building long-lasting relationships with our clients, and we are proud to have earned their trust over the years. We are constantly staying up-to-date with the latest developments in the healthcare industry to provide you with the most relevant and effective solutions.
            </p>
            <h1 class="fw-bold mt-5">
                Your Partner in Managing Health Insurance Needs: Explore <a href="/" class="navbar-brand text-primary">MediHaven</a> Today
            </h1>
            <p class="lead mt-3 mb-5">
                We invite you to explore our website and learn more about our services. Whether you're an individual, a family, or a business, let MediHaven be your partner in managing your health insurance needs. Together, we can create a healthier and more secure future for you and your loved ones. Contact us today to get started on your journey towards better healthcare coverage.
            </p>
